summary: New Captain Marvel TV Spot Focuses on the Skrulls
title: New Captain Marvel TV Spot Focuses on the Skrulls
body:
New #CaptainMarvel TV Spot Focuses on the Skrulls

This morning Marvel released a new Captain Marvel TV spot, and this one focuses on the threat faced by Carol Danvers in the movie.

Titled “Trust”, the spot puts a heavy focus on that you can’t trust anyone…because anyone can be a Skrull. With this angle, it could be possible that Marvel really is using Captain Marvel to setup a future Secret Invasion storyline in the MCU…
